org.jsapar.parse

Class AbstractParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsapar.parse.AbstractParser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TextParser, XmlParser, XmlParser

    public class AbstractParser
extends Object
    Abstract base class for all parsers. The default error handling is to throw an exception upon the first error that occurs. You can however change that behavior by adding an ErrorEventListener. There are several implementations to choose from such as RecordingErrorEventListener or ThresholdRecordingErrorEventListener, or you may implement your own..
